{"tid":2126724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不信本土疫苗 朝精英搶訂外國貨","createTime":"2020-07-27T04:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T04:30:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68da7f19746a8da82c502e665fac5cf9bb98c22c","tid":2126724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200727/BBZXRV4MUOEK6TZRUWZKWXYXEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200727%2FBBZXRV4MUOEK6TZRUWZKWXYXEE%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=3b83b91f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200727%2FBBZXRV4MUOEK6TZRUWZKWXYXEE%2F&h=614c9c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200727/BBZXRV4MUOEK6TZRUWZKWXYXEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不信本土疫苗 朝精英搶訂外國貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J4dnwYq4Aj4W3ry1jnUBtLep6gw=/640x209/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S74CO274COQDTSCMRT5XAZZFKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ4dnwYq4Aj4W3ry1jnUBtLep6gw%3D%2F640x209%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS74CO274COQDTSCMRT5XAZZFKE.jpg&h=6db3481a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正恩前日舉行緊急會議應對疫情。路透社<br />\n<br />\n北韓聲稱在武漢肺炎疫苗研究工作上有突破性進展，不過當地精英已率先預訂國外研發的疫苗，更稱「美元不是問題」。消息指是由於北韓精英對本土研發的疫苗沒有信心。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：靠近分界線 兩韓經濟合作象徵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲稱研發疫苗有突破<br />\n<br />\n北。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。事實上不少北韓人對官方聲稱疫苗研發現突破都有質疑，指大部份平民連基本藥物都不會接觸到。而且政府2月時向醫院提供病毒檢測工具，聲稱是本地研發，不過就被醫生發現是外國產品的仿製品。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，「不少人質疑為何當局一方面聲稱國內一宗確診個案也沒有，一方面又搜刮所有可動用的資源趕工興建平壤綜合醫院」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。「北韓政府沒能力照顧人民的現實製造了民間對政府的不信任。人民已預料只能靠自己」。<br />\n<br />\n當地精英相信政府或可欺騙普通人，但他們自己就不會這麼容易上當。北韓消息人士透露，「越來越多高官和商界精英向國外朋友付錢，拜託他們一有疫苗面世，不論價錢立即搶購。有指中國商人不斷接到來自平壤及邊境地區的查詢，問是否已有疫苗面世」。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《每日朝鮮》"},{"pid":"1e0162cc77bad14c6695e0a1d350ededdcade9ac","tid":2126724,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw9dfer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw9dfer.gif&h=3c3c2223&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fg5Px07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg5Px07.gif&h=8b60eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f37edded7f12c1d89a4b8a2b4717d46b58392535","tid":2126724,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"真係唔明北泡咁都仲有二千五萬人口<br />\n而家有冇一半奶嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}